					<span class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 text-sm font-bold">2</span>
					User Conduct & Community Standards
				</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-700 mb-3">As a member of the CodePals community, you agree to:</p>
				<ul class="space-y-2 ml-8 text-slate-700">
					<li>Treat all members with respect and dignity</li>
					<li>Communicate in a professional and constructive manner</li>
					<li>Refrain from harassment, discrimination, or hateful behavior of any kind</li>
					<li>Foster an inclusive environment for developers of all backgrounds and experience levels</li>
					<li>Follow our Code of Conduct in all community interactions</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<!-- Section 3 -->
			<section>
				<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 text-sm font-bold">3</span>
					Prohibited Behavior
				</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-700 mb-3">You agree not to engage in any of the following activities:</p>
				<ul class="space-y-2 ml-8 text-slate-700">
					<li>Harassment, intimidation, or bullying of other members</li>
					<li>Discrimination based on gender, race, ethnicity, religion, sexual orientation, or any protected characteristic</li>
					<li>Hate speech or offensive language targeting individuals or groups</li>
					<li>Spam, scams, or malicious behavior</li>
					<li>Impersonation or misrepresentation of identity</li>
					<li>Sharing of private information without consent (doxxing)</li>
					<li>Any behavior that violates our Code of Conduct</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<!-- Section 4 -->
			<section>
				<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 text-sm font-bold">4</span>
					Account Responsibility
				</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
					You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for all activities that occur under your account. You agree to notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account.
				</p>
			</section>

			<!-- Section 5 -->
			<section>
				<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 text-sm font-bold">5</span>
					Content & Intellectual Property
				</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
					You retain all ownership rights to content you post on CodePals. By posting, you grant CodePals a license to display your profile, contributions, and public interactions to facilitate the mentorship platform. You represent that your content does not infringe on the rights of others.
				</p>
			</section>

			<!-- Section 6 -->
