				<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 text-sm font-bold">8</span>
					Contact Us
				</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-700">
					If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us on
					<a
						href="https://github.com/codepalsio/codepalsio"
